    S.toCotangentTraceZetaSource

-- Step 122: Mellin / Fourier integral-transform reconstruction.

/--
An *integral-transform reconstruction law*: a geometric kernel whose
Mellin transform (with Fourier/Poisson duality) reconstructs the
completed zeta determinant.
