-- Step 164: transfer-operator heat deformation.

/--
A *transfer-operator* mechanism: periodic-orbit traces are the
dynamical analogue of prime-power sums; the Fredholm determinant equals
zeta.
-/
structure TransferOperatorHeatDeformation where
