  D.conditionalResult.yieldsIrrationality

-- === Phase L: The Exact Truncation Formula Qₙ = Uₙ ===
-- The dyadic-recursive quotient with one ternary correction,
--   Qₙ = num(Cₙ / (C_{⌊n/2⌋}C_{⌊n/4⌋}C_{⌊n/8⌋}⋯C_{⌊n/3⌋})),
