theorem topLayer_total_cost_wins :
    (3 : ℝ) + 5 / 6 < tinyModeThresholdValue := by
  unfold tinyModeThresholdValue
  norm_num

/--
**PROVED — the worst observed case still wins.** Even the worst sampled
`log Uₙ/n ≈ 0.850992` (over `56 ≤ n ≤ 5000`) gives total
`3 + 0.850992 ≈ 3.851`, still below the threshold `3.9113`.
