/--
**Named target — the exact truncation formula.** The ternary-dyadic
quotient `Qₙ = num(Cₙ / (C_{⌊n/2⌋}C_{⌊n/4⌋}⋯C_{⌊n/3⌋}))` equals exactly
the top-prime layer `Uₙ` for all `n ≥ 56` (validated to `n = 5000`,
finitely many exceptions below 56) — a provable Chebyshev/carry
identity.
