/-- **PROVED — within any root-of-unity-extractor diagnosis, when
`N > 4` the γ contribution vanishes.** This is the major structural
simplification: γ is in the bridge, but NOT in the projector. -/
theorem rouExtractor_gamma_cancels
    (D : RootOfUnityExtractorDiagnosis) (hN : 4 < D.primitivity.N) :
    ∑ j ∈ Finset.range D.primitivity.N, (omegaN D.primitivity.N ^ 4) ^ j = 0 :=
