**Named record — pentagonal cyclotomic pair multiplier.** The
multiplier `Φ₅(2n)·Φ₁₀(2n)/(2n)⁸` shifts the ζ(5) channel into a
controlled even ladder `1 + 1/(4n²) + 1/(16n⁴) + ⋯`.
