`[−5, 6, −3, −3, 9, 2]` for `[S₁, S₂, S₃, S₄, S₅, ζ(5)]`. -/
def pslqRelationVector : List ℤ := [-5, 6, -3, -3, 9, 2]

/--
**Named target — the alternating central-binomial identity.**
`ζ(5) = 2·∑(-1)^{n+1}/(n^5·C(2n,n))
        − (5/2)·∑(-1)^{n+1}·H^{(2)}_{n−1}/(n^3·C(2n,n))`.
