/--
**Named target — the NEW nonalternating central-binomial identity.**
PSLQ relation: `−5S₁ + 6S₂ − 3S₃ − 3S₄ + 9S₅ + 2ζ(5) = 0`.
Equivalently `ζ(5) = (5/2)S₁ − 3S₂ + (3/2)S₃ + (3/2)S₄ − (9/2)S₅`.
Verified to residual 10⁻¹²⁰. NOT a previously-known identity.
-/
