**Named target — Identity 16: root-of-unity projector.**
For `N > 4`, `|ρ| < 1`, `ω_N = e^{2πi/N}`:
  ζ(5) = lim_{N→∞} (1/(N·ρ⁴))·∑_{j=0}^{N-1} G(ρ·ω_N^j)·ω_N^{-4j}
       = lim_{N→∞} −(1/(N·ρ⁴))·∑_{j=0}^{N-1} ψ(1−ρ·ω_N^j)·ω_N^{-4j}
The PROVED ingredients are in Phase LXXIV (γ-cancellation, discrete
orthogonality).
-/
structure RootOfUnityProjectorIdentity where
  proven_in_phase_LXXIV : Prop

/--
**Named target — Identity 17: rational-kernel alias.**
  ∑_{m≥0} ζ(5+mN)·ρ^{mN} = ∑_{r≥1} r^{N−5}/(r^N − ρ^N).
For ρ = 1/2: `ζ(5) = lim_{N→∞} 2^N·∑ r^{N−5}/((2r)^N − 1)`.
-/
structure RationalKernelAliasIdentity where
