/--
The **last-row + carry-operator + conjectures diagnosis**.
PROVED:
  • `displayedBin`, `carryAtChamber` definitions.
  • `displayedBin_plus_carry_eq`: exact conservation.
  • `displayedBin_lt_M`: residue bounded by capacity.
  • `choose_le_n_pow_k`: PROVED upper bound `C(n,k) ≤ n^k`.
