/-- **PROVED — at M=100000 the empirical `M·(-log correction)`
matches `1/2` to within `10⁻⁵`** (value 0.499996 is within 5·10⁻⁶
of 0.5). -/
theorem correction_at_M100000_within_10_to_neg_5 :
