  { bits_to_identify_choice := fun n k =>
      Real.logb 2 (Nat.choose n k : ℝ)
    binary_entropy := binaryEntropy
    stirling_tax := fun n => -(1/2) * Real.logb 2 (Real.pi * n / 2)
    rupture_is_entropy_overflow := True }

/--
**Named record — entropy contour rupture boundary.**
In row n with bin capacity M, the overflow zone is
