--   • The probe arithmetic: at probe z_ε = a + (b-ε)·I for pole
--     ρ = a + b·I, we have z_ε - ρ = -ε·I.
--   • Im(m / (-ε·I)) = m/ε (PROVED via Complex.div_im).
--   • The escape inequality 0 < m/ε - K (PROVED with bounded background).
--   • Polynomial-form upper-root escape: at the probe below an upper
