/-- Council C020 — Inverse expansion.
`λ⁻¹` generates expanding dynamics: `‖λ⁻¹‖ > 1`.
Status: **alias** over `norm_lambdaG1_inv_gt_one`. -/
theorem council_C020_inverse_expansion : 1 < ‖lambdaG1_inv‖ :=
