/-- Council C021 — Invariant geometric sum.
`Σ p₀ · λⁿ = p₀ / (1 − λ)`. Status: **alias** over
`law_of_invariant_geometric_sum`. -/
theorem council_C021_invariant_geometric_sum (p0 : ℂ) :
