  rw [criticalReflection_fixed_iff_re_eq_half]
  unfold criticalShift
  simp [Complex.add_re, Complex.mul_re]

/-- **Self-adjointness forces zeta-pole mirror fixedness.**
For any bounded Hilbert–Pólya bridge `B`, every critical-strip pole of
the xi-like reciprocal response is fixed by the critical reflection:
