| `OverflowOperator.ArgumentPrincipleWitness`              | `∮ Λ[f] = 2πi(Z − P)`                                          |
| `OverflowOperator.MomentTowerWitness`                    | `∮ z^k Λ[f]` = power sum + Newton reconstruction                |
| `OverflowOperator.OverflowOperatorCalculus`              | algebraic + analytic bundle                                     |
| `OverflowOperator.ArgumentPrinciplePrinciple`            | universal Argument-principle hypothesis (`Prop`)                |
| `OverflowOperator.MomentTowerPrinciple`                  | universal moment-tower hypothesis (`Prop`)                      |
| `OverflowOperator.overflowOperatorCalculus_of_principles`| capstone transfer theorem                                       |

This tier turns the **logarithmic derivative `f'/f`** into a calculus
